# ESA Report Generator — Architecture (Streamlit + docxtpl)

## Current state (repo is built — extend, do not greenfield)

**Primary use case:** Alberta O&G **Phase I ESA** for **Ecoventure Inc.** (`consultant_name` / `company` = Ecoventure Inc.). Samples: `samples/phase1_alberta_data.xlsx` + `samples/phase1_alberta_template.docx`.

**Authoritative docs:** [docs/README.md](docs/README.md) · [docs/00-start-here.md](docs/00-start-here.md) (consultants) · Phase I: [docs/11-alberta-phase1-esa.md](docs/11-alberta-phase1-esa.md) · SED 002: [docs/20-aer-sed002-phase1-esa.md](docs/20-aer-sed002-phase1-esa.md) · Profiles: [docs/13-flexible-report-profiles.md](docs/13-flexible-report-profiles.md) · Deploy: [docs/14-deployment.md](docs/14-deployment.md) · Power Automate: [docs/15-power-automate-guide.md](docs/15-power-automate-guide.md) · User testing: [docs/12-testing-with-your-documents.md](docs/12-testing-with-your-documents.md)

**Setup (required before scripts):**

```powershell
.\.venv\Scripts\Activate.ps1
pip install -r requirements.txt
```

Use venv `python` or `.\.venv\Scripts\python.exe` — system `python` lacks `pandas` / project deps.

**Excel sheets (exact names, case-sensitive):**

| Sheet | Phase 1 | Phase 2 | Jinja context |
|-------|---------|---------|---------------|
| `ProjectData` | Required | Required | Flat dict per data row (**row 2+**; row 1 = headers). Single report uses row 2; batch uses all non-blank rows (max 100 rows, 50 reports). |
| `LabResults` | Optional | **Required** | `lab_results` list |
| `DrillingWaste` | Optional | Optional | `drilling_waste` list (Alberta Phase I tables) |
| `StorageTanks` | Optional | Optional | `storage_tanks` list |
| `PhraseCatalog` | Optional | Optional | Phrase options + `phrase_key_selected` columns (see `phrase_resolver.py`) |
| `ReportConfig` | Optional | Optional | key/value overrides (`report_type`, `map_*`) |

**Code layout:** `app.py` + `ui/*` (Streamlit, incl. `phrase_panel`, `preflight`, `appendix_panel`) · `engine.py` (`ReportEngine`, `render_batch`) · `appendix_generator.py` (Phase I appendices D/G from `DrillingWaste`) · `phrase_resolver.py` · `report_profile.py` · `template_attachments.py` (PDF→DOCX) · `template_size.py` · `deliverable_pack.py` · `phase1_narrative.py` · `phase1_decision.py` · `sed002_compliance.py` · `phase1_markup.py` · `phase1_pdf_text.py` · `template_tools.py` · `security.py` · `provenance.py` · `schemas/report_profiles.json` (incl. `appendix_templates` per profile) · `schemas/sed002_phase1_checklist.json` · `schemas/phrase_catalog.json` · `schemas/field_contract.json` (legacy/AI) · `samples/appendices/` (D/G Word templates) · `scripts/` (`create_appendix_templates.py`) · `automate/`.

**Report profiles:** `phase1_alberta`, `phase1_devon`, `phase2_esa`, `groundwater_monitoring`, `template_driven` — see [docs/13-flexible-report-profiles.md](docs/13-flexible-report-profiles.md). Recommended fields per profile in `schemas/report_profiles.json`. Optional Excel `ReportConfig` sheet for overrides.

**Quick test:** `python scripts\test_with_your_documents.py` or `streamlit run app.py` · unit tests: `python -m unittest discover -s tests -v` (135 tests) · regression: `python scripts\health_check.py` (13 checks)

